    dc:creator "Teslenko, Valentina A." ;
    dc:date "2015" ;
    dc:title "A new species of Nemoura (Plecoptera: Nemouridae) from South of the Russian Far East" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.244669>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.244670> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.244669>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 4. Nemoura khasanensis sp. n.: 1. Male abdominal tip, dorsal. 2. Male abdominal tip, ventral. 3. Epiproct, dorsal. Mpmoveable prong, R—apex of the ring of the ventral sclerite. 4. Epiproct, ventral. Scale (mm): 1, 2 = 0.3; 3, 4 = 0.1." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/244669/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.244670>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5 – 7. 5 – 6. Nemoura khasanensis sp. n.: 5. Female, terminalia, cleared, ventral. 6. Vaginal complex, cleared, dorsal. Rreceptacle, O—oviduct, Sh—collar-like shield, CVs—cap-shaped vaginal sclerite, Rp—finger – shaped roughened pocket, P—beanshaped pouch, Go—genital opening, RVs—rounded vaginal sclerite, Vl—finger like vaginal lobe, TVs—transverse vaginal sclerite, Sp—subgenital plate as an inverted letter “ T ”. 7. Nemora longicercia. Epiproct, dorsal. Al—apical membranous lobe. Scale (mm): 5 = 0.3; 6 = 0.1." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/244670/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

